    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and 8,400 RPM redline. Power is delivered via a tactile 6-speed manual transmission to the rear wheels through an M Variable Differential Lock. The chassis maintains its composure with factory Electronic Damping Control (EDC), providing adjustable damping rates to suit various road surfaces. Recent maintenance includes a comprehensive inspection of the rod bearings and throttle actuators to ensure long-term mechanical integrity. The subframe and VANOS system remain in robust working order. While exhibiting minor aesthetic patina expected of a well-loved machine, the powertrain remains tight, offering the visceral induction note and linear torque curve that define this final era of atmospheric M-cars.",
      "price": 34500.0,
